high_descs: Turn to the desk on the right.
Pick up the book with a light blue colored cover, in between another book and the laptop.
Exit the room through the door on the right and continue ahead into the bedroom, then approach the bed from the side with the table.
Place the book down on the bed.
Exit the room through the way you came in to return to the desk where you picked up the book.
Pick up the second book from the table.
Return to the bed where you placed the first book down.
Place the second book down next to the first book on the bed.
anns.task_desc: Place two books down on a bed.

high_descs: Turn right to reach the desk.
Pick up the blue book on the right of the laptop.
Turn right to head out the room and  walk across the passage to reach the bedroom and head to the bed.
Put the book on the bed.
Turn right to exit the room and walk to the room across the passage to reach the desk on the right.
Pick up the book on the right of the laptop.
Turn right to head out the room and  walk across the passage to reach the bedroom and head to the bed.
Put the book on the bed behind the other book.
anns.task_desc: Put two books on the bed.

Take that book and move to the bed.
The book is placed on the bed.
